0.0.2

* speed up file uploads by using larger packets (increases max packet size from 128B to 8KB)
* reduced delay when receiving packets
* file uploads in background
* get rid of ncurses and switched to rust termion
* get rid of "transmitting" and "ack" messages; instead send status is displayed next to the message
* requires at Rust >=1.31.0 (edition 2018)
* updated versions of dependencies
